{"tid":1508204,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"一個P牌,請大家用幾數分鐘去投票,爭取BNO 平權都有啲好處","createTime":"2019-08-26T12:38:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-08T01:56:04.000Z","uid":269251,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"f9dbe65006421d9cf70c58a985d12950c2d99ef5","tid":1508204,"uid":269251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T12:38:05.000Z","msg":"爭取BNO 平權如接納並討論的話,英國下及上議院都會討論同時亦將會提到香港情況,議員知多啲就會講多啲,留意新聞嘅人就會多啲人知而去了解香港的事,BNO平權是否通過不重要,但英國下及上議院去討論過程先係重點,請大家用幾數分鐘去投票支持平權.<br />\n<a href=\"https://petition.parliament.uk/petitions/244402?fbclid=IwAR18t2XSAPC7XhqYg-nwdgyEgvuwXziO01vxCuZH2rgOq9IjGxx1OlXr3eg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetition.parliament.uk%2Fpetitions%2F244402%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR18t2XSAPC7XhqYg-nwdgyEgvuwXziO01vxCuZH2rgOq9IjGxx1OlXr3eg&d=qutgakuQBXsObMwiKtfrsXKg77Sy3LnB9Oyli8DN%2Bms%3D&h=dc4c56c2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petition.parliament.uk/petitions/244402?fbclid=IwAR18t2XSAPC7XhqYg-nwdgyEgvuwXziO01vxCuZH2rgOq9IjGxx1OlXr3eg</a>"},{"pid":"9d5a15d994a13e57a21d94b66991a3feda2218fd","tid":1508204,"uid":33930,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T12:52:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4B5ZOzj.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4B5ZOzj.gif&h=0e4bb77e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n九月一號下午一點機場見<br />\n<br />\n901機場和你塞 Channel<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=qutgakuQBXsObMwiKtfrsXKg77Sy3LnB9Oyli8DN%2Bms%3D&h=27ac0331\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyou</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 公海<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyouopen&d=qutgakuQBXsObMwiKtfrsXKg77Sy3LnB9Oyli8DN%2Bms%3D&h=4eac569d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyouopen</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 宣傳<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyoupromote\" data-sr-url=\"https://